resources.string: Mena he pai koe ki tenei taupānga kua whakawhanaketia e au, tena koa tirohia mai te hoko i aku taupānga takoha.
Kaore e mahia e te taupānga takoha, engari ko taau koha e whakaatu mai ka mutu taku waatea ki te whakawhanake koreutu, kaore he panui-a-ringa e manakohia ana.
Mena he pai koe ki tenei taupānga kua whakawhanakehia e au, tena koa ka whakaarohia te hoko i taku taupānga whakahou.

Kei roto i te taupānga whakahou nga pouakataki mo te tohu ka rere koe i nga nama me nga putea ranei, na to hoko ka whakaatu mai i taku waa ki te whakawhanake i te koreutu, kaore he kaupapa whakatairanga hei whakamana.
